  "title": "L2 PreSchool English Teacher",
  "description": "<h4><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, supervise and deliver the curriculum/program in accordance with the policies, guidelines, frameworks and philosophy of MindChamps</li>\n  <li>Prepare and implement programs and age-appropriate teaching aids</li>\n  <li>Keep accurate records of the children’s progress and address the children’s educational and developmental needs individually</li>\n  <li>Complete the progress reports of the children for each semester and prepare developmental portfolio for every child</li>\n  <li>Communicate with parents via the Parent APP, newsletters and parent-teacher conferences</li>\n  <li>Meet parents to address any concerns</li>\n  <li>Use positive discipline techniques at all times</li>\n  <li>Guide and supervise the Assistant Teacher in the classroom</li>\n  <li>Render basic first aid as and when necessary</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the upkeep of teaching resources, arrangement, appearance, decorations and learning environment of the classroom</li>\n  <li>Be familiarised with all working curriculum documents, handbooks and policy manuals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Early Childhood Care &amp; Education–Teaching (DECCE-T)</li>\n  <li>Fluent in English (spoken and written) as lessons are conducted in English</li>\n  <li>Creative and inspiring with loving energy</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and classroom management skills</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in educational development</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Permanent positions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive remuneration and benefits package</li>\n  <li>Comprehensive teacher's training on the depth of the MindChamps curriculum will be provided</li>\n  <li>Ample opportunities for personal growth and career development</li>\n  <li>21 days of Annual Leave entitlement for successful candidates</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nearest MRT Station: Caldecott MRT (Circle/Thomson-East Coast Line)</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
